Tamar Marash

We are delighted to announce that we are conducting our first closing of AL=
F III fund, the 3rd series of Funds in our Global Asset Based Lending Strat=
egy with total committed and investable capital of $480M at closing.

As a reminder, ALF III funds seek to provide investors with attractive ongo=
ing current income and potential for capital gains through asset-based lend=
ing transactions to finance assets originated by Tech enabled Lenders (aka =
FinTech lenders) across US, Western Europe, U.K and Australia.

We are also excited to draw your attention to the first capital call follow=
ing the execution of our first transactions in ALF III fund.
